# Cave Dwarf

- old dwarf wants us to leave until he can clean up
- barraque clanghammer lives in the vault and was not expecting visitors
- wants us to explain why we are there
- does not trust us at all and seems to want to get rid of us
- aquamarine stone around his head
- dwarf really wants us to leave
- esevale wants us to find someone the dwarf will remember in order to convince him to give us the gold
- clan Melairkyn Clan etched on leather wrapping around the weapon
- mace supposed to fight balagos the red dragon
- clan has faded from existence and mace long forgotten
- stone golem broke down to dust and faded